OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fevening with occasional late sunshine.
OL,7,FCloud increasing overnight to bring
OL,8,Fsome scattered light showers before
OL,9,Fdawn. Northerly winds increasing fresh
OL,10,Fto strong.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FNortherly winds bringing
OL,13,Fmainly cloudy skies and a few light
OL,14,Fshowers, though most of these will be
OL,15,Fconfined to Shetland.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,18,Fmainly dry with some limited brighter
OL,19,Fspells and light winds. Tuesday and
OL,20,FWednesday cloudy with occasional areas
OL,21,Fof rain crossing from the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
